data.eml:eml: Larval morphology of three species of Anteoninae (Hymenoptera, Dryinidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Bückle, Christoph (2017): Larval morphology of three species of Anteoninae (Hymenoptera, Dryinidae). Zootaxa 4320 (3): 470-486, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4320.3.4
